## Relationship with the harness family

harness-design is the **UI design** member of the harness family, focused on looks good and works well. Other members collaborate via document handoffs:

| Family member | Responsibility | Handoff method |
|---------|------|---------|
| harness-pm | Product research / market / PRD | Produces `docs/handoff/pm-to-design.md` → consumed by this framework |
| harness-design (this framework) | UI / visual / interaction design | Produces `docs/handoff/design-to-solo.md` → handed off to engineering |
| harness-solo | Engineering development | Consumes this framework's design specs |
| harness-growth | Content / SEO / data (on demand) | Consumes this framework's output |

**Handoff protocol**: see handoff documents under the `docs/handoff/` directory. Drop them in manually to be recognized by the design-brief skill.

